data.description: WELCOME HOME! This stunning 3 bedrooms 2 1/2 bath townhome will amaze you with its features. Cozy up to a remote controlled fireplace in the living room. The open concept kitchen has chrome/black appliances, dark cabinets, granite countertops, backsplash, and a breakfast bar. The dining room is equipped with a set of beautiful French Double Doors that open inside and out to a private fenced in backyard for your enjoyment. The spacious master bedroom has a double vanity ensuite, separate shower and large walk-in closet. The flooring is carpet, wood, and tile.     NO BLIND OFFERS, PLEASE!
